{"tid":444418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國公安抓人 罪名太狂讓網友都跪了","createTime":"2017-10-22T13:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T13:32:10.000Z","uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32e8563a2787b41f02cc02de14b871ebf5ea5aa3","tid":444418,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:25:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2230399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2230399&d=ytPBNWVX11MqgvXu93vcRaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=eafa85db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2230399&h=dc7b4251\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2230399</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-10-22 20:14<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國昆明市公安局發出的一份「逮捕通知書」近日在網路瘋傳，因為當中逮捕民眾的罪名，竟填上「符合逮捕條件罪」，等於沒有理由；該份逮捕通知書流傳到台灣網路論壇PTT，網友直呼實在太狂，根本是「莫須有」罪名的現代版。<br />\n<br />\n根據流出的逮捕通知書顯示的資訊，該通知書是由中國昆明市公安局盤龍分局發出，內容載明，張姓公安經盤龍區人民檢察院批准，於2017年10月20日20時對涉嫌「符合逮捕條件罪」的張姓民眾執行逮捕，並將人羈押在昆明市看守所。<br />\n<br />\n該份公文流傳到PTT引起熱烈討論，網友直呼這個罪名實在太狂，「好歹想個理由吧」、「說你符合就符合」、「習包子要你被關你就被關了」，有人妙喻，這就是「莫須有」罪名的現代版；另方面有網友指出，「符合逮捕條件罪」其實就是預防性羈押，台灣也有類似做法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpssuij8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpssuij8.jpg&h=d61c5bfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9938f907484782ad3e1d0b2d9d38b2e965e7bc7","tid":444418,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"這就是中國.jpg"},{"pid":"096ceff92d60aa6dad9f3f89066325a2e72c2419","tid":444418,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知幾時會係香港見到呢個情況呢"},{"pid":"636a546506df714b68